      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GALBA STACEY (1) flew the lids with a sensational early split and led throughout to score an impressive win by half a length over 300m at Murray Bridge (16.73). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Looks the one to beat. RIGHT SIDE UP (2) could manage only seventh at Angle Park last time but turned heads when posting a dominant 19.35 over 342m at Angle Park three starts back. Has the ability and can find winning form again. DANYO'S HENRY (8) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (16.86) at Murray Bridge. Solid record here at this trip including three wins. Key player if finds best. AFIRE (6) placed last time (16.98) at this track in a Invitation, finishing second and beaten 1.5 lengths. Has already won four times from this draw.",
